quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,"Jewe Allah, Ndarahiye ku bihuhusi bitumura ivumbi;"
  51,2,"No ku bicu vy’imvura;"
  51,3,"No ku bwato bugendera mw’ibahari vyoroshe;"
  51,4,"No ku bamalayika bashikana amabwirizwa y’Imana Allah ku biremwa;"
  51,5,"Ko vy’ukuri izurwa ry’ibiremwa musezeranirwa ari iry’ukuri, ritegerezwa gushika;"
  51,6,"N’uko mu vy’ukuri iharurirwa n’impera ku vyo mwakoze, bitegerezwa kuba!"
  51,7,"Jewe Allah, Ndarahiye kw’ijuru ryaremwe mu buryo butangaje;"
  51,8,"Ko mu vy’ukuri, mwebwe abahakanyi muri ba mahindagu ku vyerekeye ukwemera Qor’ani hamwe n’Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah);"
  51,9,"Higizwa kure ya Qor’ani n’Intumwa, uwigijwe kure y’ukuvyemera mu kwirengagiza ivyemezo vy’Imana Allah."
  51,10,"Harakavumwa rero abahakanyi bibwira ibitari ukuri;"
  51,11,"Abimonogoje mu buhakanyi, bagoswe mu bugarariji;"
  51,12,"Babaza bitangaza mu ntumbero yo guhakana bati: “Mbega umusi w’iharurirwa n’impera, uzoshika ryari!”."
  51,13,"Umusi w’iharurirwa n’impera, ni umusi bahanishijwe umuriro;"
  51,14,"Maze bakabwirwa bati: “Nimuhonje ibihano vyanyu, ari na vyo mwahora mwihutira gusaba kw’isi ko mwohabwa”."
  51,15,"Mu vy’ukuri abagamburukiramana, kuri uwo musi bazoba bari mu mirima itotahaye yo mu Bwami bw’ijuru, irimwo n’amazi y’imbizi atemba;"
  51,16,"Maze bakirane urweze n’akanyamuneza, impano bahawe n’Imana yabo Rurema Allah, mu vy’ukuri n’imbere yuko bahabwa nya mpano, bahora ari abagwaneza mu bugamburutsi bwabo kw’isi;"
  51,17,"Ni gake baryama mw’ijoro ku kubera ugusenga;"
  51,18,"No mu bucagucagu, barasaba Imana Allah imbabazi ku vyaha vyabo;"
  51,19,"No mu matungo yabo, baratanga ishikanwa-bwirizwa n’imperezwa, bagahereza umukene asega n’uwipfa agasoni ntasege."
  51,20,"Burya mw’iremwa ry’isi, harimwo ivyemezo vyerekana ubushobozi n'ububasha vy’Imana Allah, ku bemera ata guhigimanga ko Allah ari Yo Mana y’ukuri Ibwirijwe gusengwa, n’uko Muhamadi ari Intumwa yayo."
  51,21,"Bantu! No mw’iremwa ryanyu nyene, harimwo ivyemezo vyerekana ko Imana Allah ari Yo Yonyene Yabaremye, gutyo Ikaba ari Yo Ibwirijwe gusengwa ari Imana Imwe Rudende Itabangikanywa. Mbega none ntimubona ngo mutegere ukuri!"
  51,22,"Ibibabeshaho hamwe n’ivyo musezeranirwa: vyaba ivyiza canke ibibi, amahirwe canke amarushwa, vyose biri mw’ijuru, vyaragezwe kandi biranditswe."
  51,23,"Ku kubera ivyo vyose rero, Ndarahiye Jewe Allah ku kuba ari Jewe Rurema Yaremye ijuru n’isi, ko ivyo Nabasezeraniye vyose, ari ukuri mudakwiye kugirako amakenga; nka kurya mutagira amakenga ko muvuga mugatomora."
  51,24,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Mbega warashikiriwe n’inkuru y’abashitsi bubashwe mu bamalayika bigeze kugendera Ibrahimu (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah);"
  51,25,"Igihe binjira kwa Ibrahimu bagaca baramutsa bati: “Nimugire amahoro”; maze na we akabishura ati: “Nimusangwe amahoro, emwe bashitsi ntamenye abo muri bo!”."
  51,26,"Ni ho yinyavya mu kigo afata ishashi y’inka inuze arayibaga, arayotsa;"
  51,27,"Araheza ayizimana ba bashitsi mu rupfasoni nta ngere ati: “Mbega ntimwokwihereza!”;"
  51,28,"Ibrahimu amaze kubona ko ba bashitsi badafunguye, vyaramuteye ubwoba. Nya ntumwa zimaze kubona ko Ibrahimu yagize ubwoba, zahavuye mu kumuhumuriza zimubwira ziti: “Ntugire ubwoba namba! Twebwe turi abamalayika”. Ni ho rero baca banamushikiriza n’agakuru keza yuko umukenyezi wiwe Sarah azokwibaruka umwana w’incabwenge mw’idini yitwa Is-haka."
  51,29,"Umukenyezi wa Ibrahimu Sarah aho yumviye inkuru yuko azokwibaruka umwana, yaregereye hafi yabo, maze yikubita kw’itama yitangaza ati: “Bishoboka gute ko novyara kandi ndi umukecuru, nkaba ndi n’ingumba!”."
  51,30,"Ba bashitsi b’abamalayika bamwishuye bati: “Iyo nkuru tuyikubwiye nk’uko yavuzwe n’Imana yawe Rurema Allah Yo Mushoboravyose; mu vy’ukuri Imana Allah, ni Intungane mu vyo Ikora, Nyenubumenyikurivyose”."
  51,31,"Ibrahimu (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah) yabwiye nya ntumwa mu bamalayika ati: “Ntumwa z’Imana! None mwoba mugenzwa n’amaki?”;"
  51,32,"Na zo zirishura ziti: “Mu vy’ukuri, twarungitswe ku bantu b’abanyavyaha bimonogoje mw’igarariza;"
  51,33,"Kugira tubahanishe amabuye yokeje;"
  51,34,"Nya mabuye ariko ikimenyetso kivuye ku Mana yawe Rurema Allah, yagenewe abimonogoje mu bugarariji bagenzwa n’ubwononyi kw’isi”."
  51,35,"Ni ho rero Twebwe Allah, Twakura mu gacimbiri k’abantu ba Luutwi, abemeramana;"
  51,36,"Eka mbere ntitwanasanze muri nya gacimbiri, kiretse umuhana umwe gusa w’abemeramana, ukaba wari uwa Luutwi (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah);"
  51,37,"Muri ko, Twahasize ikimenyetso c’igihano Twabahaye, cerekana ubushobozi bw’Imana Allah bwo guhana, ku bantu batinya ibihano vyayo bibabaza."
  51,38,"No mw’irungikwa rya Musa kwa Firawuni n’abunganizi biwe, igihe Tumurungikana Aayah n’ivyemezo bigaragara, harimwo Aayah n’inkebuzo ku bantu batinya ibihano bibabaza vy’Imana Allah."
  51,39,"Firawuni yaragenjeje umugongo arirengagiza ukuri ku kwishimira inguvu ziwe, maze avuga ati: “Musa, ni umurozi canke ni umukehabwenge yeruye!”."
  51,40,"Ni ho rero Twafata Firawuni n’ingabo ziwe, Duca Tubaterera mw’ibahari. Firawuni yari yakoze ibituma atabwako imiragwe ashavuriwe n’Imana Allah."
  51,41,"No mw’ihonywa rya Bene Aadi, harimwo Aayah n’inkebuzo ku wutegera, igihe Twabarungikira igihuhusi gitema kigatongora;"
  51,42,"Nta kintu na kimwe nya gihuhusi caciyeko, kiretse ko cagisiga ari ubunywenywe."
  51,43,"No mw’ihanwa rya Bene Thamuudi, harimwo Aayah n’inkebuzo, igihe Intumwa yabo Swalehe (nyakugira amahoro y’Imana Allah) yababwira iti: “Nimuryoherwe mu zanyu imisi itatu itarenga ntirenguke mu kurindira urwanyu ko rushika”."
  51,44,"Bene Thamuudi baragabitanije kw’ibwirizwa ry’Imana yabo Rurema Allah, baca bahitanwa n’igihano c’umuriro amaso mu yandi;"
  51,45,"Ntibashoboye no guhaguruka ngo babihunge bitarashika, canke ngo bavyikuremwo, eka mbere n’iyo bahunga ntibari kubirokoka."
  51,46,"Twaranahoneje abantu ba Nuhu hambere yabo. Mu vy’ukuri abantu ba Nuhu, bari n’abantu b’ibigaba birenga ku mabwirizwa y’Imana Allah."
  51,47,"N’ijuru ryegereye isi, Twarariremye maze Turaritunganya, kugira riyibere igisenge kiyikingira, kandi mu vy’ukuri Turanaryagura;"
  51,48,"N’isi, Twarayigize nk’isaso kugira ibiremwa biyiturureko, ni Twebwe rero Abeza b’abasasa."
  51,49,"No mu bwoko bw’ibiremwa vyose, Twaremye bibiribibiri bitandukanye mu ndemo; nk’igitsina-gabo n’igitsina-gore, kugira mwibuke ubushobozi n'ububasha vy’Imana Allah, muheze mwikebuke."
  51,50,"Bantu! Enda rero nyabuna nimuhungire ibihano vy’Imana Allah, mu kwirukira ku mpuhwe zayo, maze mwemere mwongere mugamburukire Imana Allah hamwe n’Intumwa yayo. Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe, ndi Umugabisha ku bihano vyayo, atomora amabwirizwa yayo."
  51,51,"Ntimukanabangikanye Imana Allah mu vyo mukora vyose mu kuyisenga n’iyindi mana. Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe, ndi Umugabisha ku bihano vyayo, atomora amabwirizwa yayo."
  51,52,"Nk’uko rero Abakorayishi bahakanye Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah) bakavuga bati: “Muhamadi, ni umwivuzi w’amazina, canke umurozi, canke umukehabwenge”; ni ko n’imigwi y’abantu bo hambere yabo yabigenjeje, ntiyigeze irungikirwa Intumwa n’imwe, kiretse ko yavuga nk’ukwo nyene, bituma Tuyihana."
  51,53,"Mbega yemwe! Abo hambere, boba basigiye abo mu nyuma zabo iragi ryo guhakana Intumwa muri ubwo buryo nyene! Ahubwo rero mbere, bo ni abantu biganza bakagarariza, bagahuza umutima w’ubugarariji n’akagagazo, gutyo bagasusa no mu buryo bwo kugarariza."
  51,54,"Ntumwa y’Imana! Irengagize ababangikanyamana mu kurindira itegeko riberekeye, nta n’uwogutako imiragwe kuko wamaze gushikana ubutumwa;"
  51,55,"Hamwe n’ivyo rero, shishikara irarikiramana wibutsa abo warungitsweko, mu vy’ukuri ukwibutswa kuragirira akamaro abemeramana, na kare ngo uwukebura uwiwe agumizako."
  51,56,"Jewe Allah, sinaremye Amajini n’abantu Nkabarungikira n’Intumwa, atari ukugira banyiyegereze mu vyo bakora vyose banansenge batambangikanya na kimwe mu biremwa;"
  51,57,"Nta bimbeshaho ndabashakako, eka mbere nta n’imfungurwa Ndabasavye, kuko ni Jewe Mubeshaho w’ibiremwa, Nyenugutanga."
  51,58,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana Allah, ni Yo Rutunga Ibeshejeho ibiremwa vyose, Nyeninguvu, Mutananirwa."
  51,59,"Mu vy’ukuri, abirenganije mu guhakana Intumwa Muhamadi (nyakugira amahoro n’impuhwe z’Imana Allah), baragenewe umugabane w’ibihano; nk’uwagenewe bagenzi babo bahakanye hambere yabo, ntibihutire rero gusaba guhanwa, kuko bitebe bitebuke, bategerezwa guhanwa."
  51,60,"Uguhanwa nya guhanwa rero, ni ukw’abagararije Imana Allah n’Intumwa yayo, bakazohanwa kuri wa musi wabo w’izuka basezeranirwa ko bazohanwa."
